EXPRMACRO.EXPRESSION:
IIF(ISNULL(in_DATE),
IIF(in_FLAG = '-', $$EDWLowerInfDate, IIF(in_FLAG = '+', $$EDWUpperInfDate, in_DATE)),

) )
